## 2. Review Modes Mapped to Build Modes

Each build mode gets a specific review approach. The review mode determines _how_ Claude and the team member verify the work.

### Agent-Driven Builds (Apex, LWC, Objects, Fields, PermSets, FlowTests)

Claude generates code/metadata from specs. Review is code-focused and test-focused.

| Review Activity       | How                                                                                                        | Who                            |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| **Code review**       | Claude reads its own output and reports against dimensions. Team member reviews the report.                | Claude generates, team reviews |
| **Test verification** | Claude runs tests and shows assertions (not just pass/fail). Team member confirms assertions match intent. | Claude runs, team verifies     |
| **Flow scanner**      | Run `sf flow scan` on any generated flow XML. Zero violations required.                                    | Claude runs                    |
| **FLS verification**  | Claude checks permission set XML against field list in spec. Cross-reference with `sf sobject describe`.   | Claude checks                  |

**Key instruction for Claude:** When reporting test results, show the specific assertion for each test — not just "all tests pass." For security-sensitive tests (sharing, FLS, Community access), show the test setup that replicates real conditions.

### Human-Focused Builds (Screen Flows, Complex Flows in Flow Builder)

Human builds manually in Flow Builder. Claude validates each step via org queries.

| Review Activity         | How                                                                                                     | Who                           |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| **Flow scanner**        | Run `sf flow scan` after each significant save. Report violations immediately.                          | Claude runs on request        |
| **Org validation**      | `sf sobject describe`, SOQL queries, `sf data query` to verify configuration matches spec.              | Claude queries, team confirms |
| **Fault path check**    | Claude queries the flow metadata to verify fault connectors exist on all DML/action elements.           | Claude checks                 |
| **Functionality trace** | Walk through each user path verbally. Team member describes what happens; Claude verifies against spec. | Collaborative                 |

### Config-Only Builds (Reports, Dashboards, Experience Cloud, Approval Processes, Data Cloud)

Human configures in Salesforce UI. Claude assists on design and validates each step.

| Review Activity               | How                                                                                          | Who              |
| ----------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------- |
| **Step-by-step verification** | After each manual step, Claude validates via org queries (`describe`, SOQL, test execution). | Claude validates |
| **Drift detection**           | Compare org state against spec to catch missed steps or unintended side effects.             | Claude checks    |
| **Spec compliance**           | Verify each configured component against the design doc.                                     | Collaborative    |
| **Documentation**             | Generate docs for manual config that isn't source-tracked (Data Cloud, CRM Analytics).       | Claude generates |

